    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, you said \"the lower the airspeed, the higher the pressure difference\"—isn't it the other way around? Also, what kind of stuff actually causes those blockages? You said it's a big deal, so I'm assuming it's more than just a bit of dust.",
